4 Episodes): Dr. Larry Naday\n*''[[London Spy]]'' (2015, 1 Episode): Professor Marcus Shaw\n*''[[Undercover (2016 TV series)|Undercover]]'' (2016): Nick Johnson (Lead)\n*''[[Riviera (TV series)|Riviera]]'' (2017 TV Series): Robert Carver\n*''Trauma'' (2018 TV series): Jon Allerton\n*''[[The Rook (miniseries)|The Rook]]'' (2019 TV miniseries): Conrad Grantchester\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2ba4181d48 Adrian Lester] at the [[British Film Institute]]\n* {{IMDb name|0504412}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Awards for Adrian Lester\n|list =\n{{Evening Standard Theatre Award for Best Actor}} \n{{OlivierAward MusicalActor 1979\u20132000}}\n}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lester, Adrian}}\n[[Category:1968 births]]\n[[Category:English people of Jamaican descent]]\n[[Category:Alumni of the Royal Academy of Dramatic Art]]\n[[Category:Black English male actors]]\n[[Category:Critics' Circle Theatre Award winners]]\n[[Category:English male film actors]]\n[[Category:English male musical theatre actors]]\n[[Category:English male television actors]]\n[[Category:Evening Standard Award for Best Actor winners]]\n[[Category:Laurence Olivier Award winners]]\n[[Category:Officers of the Order of the British Empire]]\n[[Category:People from Birmingham, West Midlands]]\n[[Category:English male Shakespearean actors]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:English male taekwondo practitioners]]\n", "name_user": "Edwin of Northumbria", "label": "safe", "comment": "Added 1 ref.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adrian_Lester"}
